Bruce Rauner
surveyed extensive damage in the
town of Ottawa.

02:18.872 --> 02:20.107 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
GOV.

02:20.140 --> 02:21.008 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
