himself up
outside the Afghan intelligence
service.

03:28.408 --> 03:31.745 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The United
States today
delivered a sharp rebuke to the
U.N. Human

03:31.778 --> 03:33.914 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
