subjected to unfair, unbalanced
and unfounded

04:09.416 --> 04:11.184 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
bias.

04:11.218 --> 04:13.854 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The critique
