20, when they then asked for the
authority

27:23.275 --> 27:25.043 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
to do the raid to Trump.

27:25.077 --> 27:28.614 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, importantly, that's why I
