company.

43:46.390 --> 43:52.497 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Mark Zuckerberg really sort of
became the
pioneer or advocate for this
approach, where,

43:52.530 --> 43:57.902 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
