video of Uber
CEO Travis Kalanick in a heated
exchange with

44:22.393 --> 44:26.497 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
an Uber driver over lowering
fares for its
black cars service.

44:26.531 --> 44:28.132 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The argument took place in
February.

44:28.165 --> 44:29.734 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: You changed the whole
business.

44:29.767 --> 44:31.135 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TRAVIS KALANICK, CEO, Uber:
What?

44:31.169 --> 44:32.103 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
What?

44:32.136 --> 44:33.104 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: You dropped the prices.

44:33.137 --> 44:34.105 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TRAVIS KALANICK: On black.

