How much is the mile now, $2.75?

44:39.143 --> 44:40.111 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
TRAVIS KALANICK: You know what?

44:40.144 --> 44:41.646 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
MAN: What?

